  section.font-1
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-2.hidden-md-down
          .perpendicular
            h2.color-9.fs-6.text-uppercase.lh-0(style="transform: translateY(36px);") My Story
        .col-12.hidden-lg-up
          h2.mb-5 My Story
        .col-lg-6
          h5.mb-4 — Story Behind Bo
          p.lead.mb-5.color-5
            | Though swimming, pools, and chlorine have been a passion of mine for many, many moons, web development is just as awesome to me. I may not have been around as long as others, but I work hard, strive to always be learning, and aim to produce the best products as possible.
            br
            br
            | I am a husband, a father, a web developer and I love every bit of it all!
            
          h5.mb-4 — Mission & Vision
          p.color-5.mb-lg-0.mb-5.lead
            | My mission is to produce the best products as possible, in the most efficient and timely manner as possible, utilizing the best technologies for the project, and always striving to learn new and better ways.
            br
            br
            | My vision is of us working together as a team in the creation of great things to help you and to help others.
        .col-lg-4.pl-lg-5
          h5.mb-0 — Started in
          .fs-5.fw-100.mb-5 2017
          h5.mb-3 — Office in
          p.fs-3.color-7.lh-1.mb-5.fw-300 North Carolina, USA
          h5.mb-3 — Services
          p.lead.color-5 Front-End and Back-End Development, Membership Sites, Personal Sites, and Commercial Sites 
      // /.row
    // /.container
